     Example 1 Setting a the Maximum  of  Log  History  Files  to
     Maintain

      This example sets to 8 the maximum number  of  log  history
     files for the server as a whole.

       asadmin> set-log-attributes --target=server com.sun.enterprise.server.logging.GFFileHandler.maxHistoryFiles=8
